{"type": "article", "id": 24298, "title": "易拆卸的桌子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-23T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150711BmjpToskES6C8AuI.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这张桌子有方便储存的特征，它的四根金属桌腿可以装在木质桌面下，不用的时候就可以把桌腿拆下来收在较小的空间里，这也意味着它容易运输。木桌面的两头有长条形的孔，是用来固定桌布的，长方形的桌布从两边穿进后就是一张干净的餐桌，增加了生活气息。设计者是来自立陶宛的学生，<a href=\"http://www.austejaplatukyte.com/#!project05/cbeq\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150709HtuRbKaEIOkFTiPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.29032258\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150709aK4boPfZtmdE0AiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150710RCGOFJ8Swqul5rUE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150710eJCDowQILxYTH1pv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150711uNQdKa7hl3RZvMX0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}